---
import Container from "@components/Container.astro";
---

<section class="animate space-y-6">
  <div class="space-y-4">
    <h5 class="font-semibold text-black">
      JobsThatSponsor cuts through the noise
    </h5>
    <p class="text-black/50">
      JobsThatSponsor is a weekly newsletter that delivers what you actually need:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black/50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h6 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Hand Curated Jobs</h6>
        <p class="text-sm text-black/70">Every Wednesday, get hand-curated visa sponsorship jobs from companies that sponsored someone in the last 6 months. Not 3 years ago. Not "we're open to it." Companies that are actively hiring international talent right now.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black/50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 7a2 2 0 012 2m4 0a6 6 0 01-7.743 5.743L11 17H9v2H7v2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2.586a1 1 0 01.293-.707l5.964-5.964A6 6 0 1121 9z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h6 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Company Insights</h6>
        <p class="text-sm text-black/70">Get detailed company insights and visa sponsorship track records. Know which companies actually sponsor and which ones just say they do.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black/50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h6 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Salary & Company Details</h6>
        <p class="text-sm text-black/70">Salary bands and company size for every role. No more guessing if a 10-person startup can afford your H1B fees.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black/50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h6 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Hiring Manager Contact</h6>
        <p class="text-sm text-black/70">We include direct hiring manager emails (when available) so you can introduce yourself like a human being instead of disappearing into another ATS system.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- 5th grid item that spans full width -->
  <div class="md:col-span-2">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black/50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h6 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Get Hired Guide & Discord Community Access</h6>
        <p class="text-sm text-black/70">Access our comprehensive "Get Hired Guide" worth $49, including professional resume templates and cold email templates. Plus, get access to our exclusive Discord community (coming soon) where you can connect with other international job seekers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 